    "QiZhenGPT-sft-20k foot_34 formulates instructions based on the content collected from the Qizhen medical knowledge base.",
    "Medical-sft foot_35 merges several Chinese and English medical datasets, including the ChatDoctor (Li et al, 2023l) and QiZhenGPTsft-20k, among others.",
    "In addition to the aforementioned, some datasets may comprise a combination of real and synthetic data or involve manual curation based on existing datasets.",
    "Chat-Doctor and HuatuoGPT-sft-data-v1 (Zhang et al, 2023b), while collecting authentic doctor-patient dialogues, incorporate conversation data generated by ChatGPT and information from a disease database.",
    "DISC-Med-SFT (Bao et al, 2023) and Medical Meadow (Han et al, 2023) meticulously select several data sources, undergoing a certain degree of reconstruction to enhance the overall quality of the datasets."
